Messer Sales May Exceed 1 Billion Euros This Year, FTD Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-07-21T06:30:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-21/messer-sales-may-exceed-1-billion-euros-this-year-ftd-reports.html
Messer Industriegase GmbH is likely
to reach sales of more than 1 billion euros ($1.4 billion) this
year earlier than forecast because of demand for industrial
gases in  China  and  Europe ,  Financial Times Deutschland  reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Stefan Messer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
